Class Employee

java.lang.Object
users.User
users.Employee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<User>, Observer, Payable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Dean, Manager, Teacher
public class Employee extends User implements Payable
The Employee class represents an employee in the university. Extends the User class and implements the Payable interface.
